	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=16203">Mindboggingly simple way to control legato (ftm inside)</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

